long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
"NFT Insights" is designed to help users monitor and detect any potential MEV, wash trading, and phishing activity across Ethereum NFTs. This tool offers an in-depth analysis of NFT transactions, providing users with valuable insights and information about the overall health and security of the NFT market. With this extension, users can stay informed and protected from any unethical activities, ensuring a safe and secure NFT trading experience.

The code is open-source and does not use any external libraries.
